## ECS Components

### `sbx::SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent`

File: `Code/SandboxApp/Sandbox/SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent.h`

Singleton (at most one instance). Holds the UUIDs parsed from `Assets/App/Config.json`. Read by `SampleUISystem`; written only by `ConfigLoaderSystem`.

| Field | Type | Description |
|-------|------|-------------|
| `m_UUIDUI1` | `pg::UUID` | UUID of the first UI element (image widget in `SandboxUI.json`) |
| `m_UUIDUI2` | `pg::UUID` | UUID of the second UI element (text widget in `SandboxUI.json`) |
| `m_DefaultFontID` | `pg::UUID` | UUID of the default font loaded by the engine resource system |
| `m_MainLayoutID` | `pg::UUID` | UUID of the root UI layout to load (`SandboxUI.json`) |

### `sbx::SampleUISingletonComponent`

File: `Code/SandboxApp/Sandbox/SampleUISingletonComponent.h`

Singleton (at most one instance). Mutable frame-state for `SampleUISystem`'s renders and ImGui controls. Created and initially populated by `SampleUISystem` on the first productive frame.

| Field | Type | Default | Description |
|-------|------|---------|-------------|
| `m_ColorQuad1` | `glm::vec3` | `(0,0,0)` | Colour of the flat quad, editable via ImGui |
| `m_PosQuad1` | `glm::vec3` | `(0,0,0)` | World-space position of Quad1, editable via ImGui |
| `m_ScaleQuad1` | `glm::vec3` | `(0,0,0)` | Scale of Quad1, editable via ImGui |
| `m_ColorQuad2` | `glm::vec3` | `(0,0,0)` | Colour tint for sprite Quad2 (unused in current draw path — sprite uses texture) |
| `m_PosQuad2` | `glm::vec3` | `(0,0,0)` | World-space position of Quad2/Sprite |
| `m_ScaleQuad2` | `glm::vec3` | `(0,0,0)` | Scale of Quad2/Sprite |
| `m_PosText` | `glm::vec3` | `(0,0,0)` | Position of the static text string, editable via ImGui |
| `m_ScaleText` | `glm::vec3` | `(0,0,0)` | Scale of the static text, editable via ImGui |
| `m_ColorText` | `glm::vec3` | `(0,0,0)` | RGB colour of the static text |
| `m_OriginQuad1` | `glm::vec3` | `(0,0,0)` | Normalised pivot of Quad1, editable via ImGui |
| `m_OriginQuad2` | `glm::vec3` | `(0,0,0)` | Normalised pivot of Quad2/Sprite |
| `m_FontID` | `pg::UUID` | null | Key into `ResourceMapSingletonComponent::m_FontMap` |
| `m_UUIDUI1` | `pg::UUID` | null | Identifies the image widget (for sprite draw look-up) |
| `m_UUIDUI2` | `pg::UUID` | null | Identifies the text widget (currently unused in draw path) |

