## Data Flow

### Startup (frame 0)

```
EntryPoint.h main()
  └── pg::CreateApplication()
        ├── Sandbox::Create()            — constructs pg::Application, opens window
        ├── World::RegisterSystem(ConfigLoaderSystem)
        └── World::RegisterSystem(SampleUISystem)
app.Run() starts the loop → World::Update(ts) called each tick
```

### Frame 1 (first World::Update)

```
World::SortSystems()                     — topological sort by DeclareAccess (runs once)

ConfigLoaderSystem::Update()
  ├── Reads Data/Assets/App/Config.json
  ├── Parses JSON, validates 4 UUID keys
  └── emplace_deferred<SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent>

SampleUISystem::Update()
  └── Guards: ResourceMapSingletonComponent absent OR SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent absent
        → returns immediately (config not yet flushed)

World::FlushDeferredRequests()
  └── SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent committed to registry
```

### Frame 2 (initialisation frame)

```
ConfigLoaderSystem::Update()
  └── SampleUIConfigSingletonComponent already present → no-op

SampleUISystem::Update()
  ├── Guards pass (both singletons present, SampleUISingletonComponent absent)
  ├── emplace_deferred<SampleUISingletonComponent>  (with initial values from config)
  ├── emplace_deferred<OrthographicCameraComponent> (1280×720, ReactsToInput=true)
  └── EmplaceEvent<pg::ui::LoadLayoutEvent>         (m_MainLayoutID → loads SandboxUI.json)

World::FlushDeferredRequests()
  └── SampleUISingletonComponent + OrthographicCameraComponent committed
  └── LoadLayoutEvent triggers UI layout parsing (engine-side UIEventSystem)
```

### Frame 3+ (steady state)

```
ConfigLoaderSystem::Update()  → no-op

SampleUISystem::Update()
  ├── Reads SampleUISingletonComponent (mutable)
  ├── EmplaceInframeEvent<DrawQuadInFrameEvent>    (Quad1 flat colour)
  ├── Iterates (BaseComponent, ImageComponent) UI entities
  │     └── Match m_UUIDUI1 → EmplaceInframeEvent<DrawSpriteInFrameEvent> (Quad2 sprite)
  ├── EmplaceInframeEvent<DrawStringInFrameEvent>  (static multi-line text)
  ├── EmplaceInframeEvent<DrawStringInFrameEvent>  (animated clock string)
  └── ImGui::Begin("Settings") — live-edits m_ColorQuad1, m_PosQuad1, m_ScaleQuad1,
                                              m_OriginQuad1, m_PosText, m_ScaleText

Renderer2DSystem (engine)
  └── Consumes DrawQuadInFrameEvent, DrawSpriteInFrameEvent, DrawStringInFrameEvent
        → batched DirectX 11 draw calls

UIRenderSystem (engine)
  └── Renders loaded UI layout entities (BaseComponent + ImageComponent/TextComponent)
```

### Shutdown

The application's `Run()` loop terminates when a `WindowCloseEvent` is received (`Application::OnWindowClose`). No SandboxApp-specific teardown is needed; all ECS state is owned by `World` and `Application`, which are destroyed via their `pg::U_Ptr` singletons.

