## Dependencies on PigeonLib Modules

| PigeonLib Module | Usage in SandboxApp |
|-----------------|---------------------|
| `pg::Application` | Base class for `Sandbox`; `Create()` factory invoked from `CreateApplication()` |
| `pg::World` / `pg::System` / `pg::SystemAccessDecl` | ECS foundation — all systems derive from `pg::System` |
| `pg::UUID` | Identity for config fields, UI element look-up, font/texture map keys |
| `pg::Timestep` / `pg::Clock` | Passed into every `Update()`; `Clock` used internally for animated clock string |
| `pg::OrthographicCameraComponent` | Created by `SampleUISystem` to register the scene camera |
| `pg::ResourceMapSingletonComponent` | Read to resolve `m_FontID` to a `pg::Font` shared pointer |
| `pg::DrawQuadInFrameEvent` | Inframe event to draw a flat coloured quad |
| `pg::DrawSpriteInFrameEvent` / `pg::Sprite` | Inframe event to draw a sub-texture sprite |
| `pg::DrawStringInFrameEvent` | Inframe event to draw MSDF text |
| `pg::ui::BaseComponent`, `pg::ui::ImageComponent`, `pg::ui::TextComponent` | Read-only iteration over loaded UI layout entities |
| `pg::ui::LoadLayoutEvent` | Fired once on init to trigger loading of `SandboxUI.json` |
| `ImGui` | Immediate-mode debug panel ("Settings") rendered inside `SampleUISystem::Update()` |
| `nlohmann::json` (`json.hpp` via PigeonLib pch) | Config file parsing in `ConfigLoaderSystem` |
| `glm` | All vector/matrix math |

